567
00:28:00,137 --> 00:28:01,470
- Ah, that's it!

568
00:28:02,345 --> 00:28:04,526
I can't take it anymore!

569
00:28:04,527 --> 00:28:05,718
- What?

570
00:28:05,719 --> 00:28:07,150
