587
00:28:45,135 --> 00:28:46,419
When is it?

588
00:28:46,420 --> 00:28:49,296
- [Holly] Tomorrow, 6:30 am.

589
00:28:49,297 --> 00:28:51,747
- Is there another one?

590
00:28:51,748 --> 00:28:53,392
- [Holly] Thursday.

591
00:28:53,393 --> 00:28:55,021
- Forget that.

592
00:28:55,022 --> 00:28:58,025
