618
00:32:12,382 --> 00:32:13,596
- Will you stop already?

619
00:32:13,597 --> 00:32:14,963
You've been calling
it every five minutes.

620
00:32:14,964 --> 00:32:15,963
- I just want to
hear their voices.

621
00:32:15,964 --> 00:32:16,999
Make sure they're okay.

622
00:32:17,000 --> 00:32:18,677
- I'm sure they're
