the festival again this year?

718
00:36:43,102 --> 00:36:44,553
- I'm looking forward to it.

719
00:36:44,554 --> 00:36:46,457
- You know, I've been
practicing real hard.

720
00:36:46,458 --> 00:36:47,845
Me, me, me.

721
00:36:47,846 --> 00:36:50,162
(Chuckling)

722
00:36:50,163 --> 00:36:52,768
