00:38:03,091 --> 00:38:05,149
- All day long?

743
00:38:05,150 --> 00:38:07,116
- We had some car trouble.

744
00:38:07,117 --> 00:38:08,216
- What is wrong with you?

745
00:38:08,217 --> 00:38:10,052
