770
00:39:04,852 --> 00:39:05,852
- You okay?

771
00:39:07,410 --> 00:39:08,410
- Yeah.

772
00:39:09,541 --> 00:39:11,029
It's just,

773
00:39:11,030 --> 00:39:13,770
